', 'https://cms.dierenbescherming.nl/assets/deKuipershoek/_800x550_crop_center-center_none/1192559-bouvy-4.jpeg?stamp=2604220935&amp;tag=xs', 'https://cms.dierenbescherming.nl/assets/deKuipershoek/_800x550_crop_center-center_none/1192559-bouvy-3.jpeg?stamp=2604220935&amp;tag=xs']::text[], 'https://ikzoekbaas.dierenbescherming.nl/asieldier/honden/4588024-bouvy'
