.jpeg?stamp=2604280908&amp;tag=xs', 'https://cms.dierenbescherming.nl/assets/dierenopvangcentrumVlaardingen/Dieren/_800x550_crop_center-center_none/IMG_3823.jpeg?stamp=2604280908&amp;tag=xs', 'https://cms.dierenbescherming.nl/assets/dierenopvangcentrumVlaardingen/_800x550_crop_center-center_none/Midnight3.jpg?stamp=2604071442&amp;tag=xs', 'https://cms.dierenbescherming.nl/assets/dierenopvangcentrumVlaardingen/Dieren/_800x550_crop_center-center_none/IMG_3829.jpeg?stamp=2604280907&amp;tag=xs']::text[], 'https://ikzoekbaas.dierenbescherming.nl/asieldier/konijnen-en-knagers/4578821-midnight-blue'
